tools.description:
Search for images in the Open Images dataset. Decompose the user's request into structured arguments — all arguments are optional, use only what applies:

• subject only: 'show me dogs' → { subject: 'Dog' }
• subject + relationship: 'dogs playing' → { subject: 'Dog', relationship: 'plays' }
• subject + relationship + object: 'person riding horse' → { subject: 'Person', relationship: 'ride', object: 'Horse' }
• query only (fallback): 'outdoor scenes' → { query: 'outdoor scenes' }

Use singular capitalized class names (Person not people, Horse not horses). If unsure of the exact name, call resolve_entity first. Common classes: Person, Animal, Dog, Cat, Car, Food, Clothing, Furniture.
